Class that, based on a selected pattern, user preferences, and (possibly) the target ontology, creates an ontology design pattern instantiation, in the form of both a) the logic axioms representing the design solution encoded in the pattern itself, and b) OPLa metadata on that solution describing the use of a pattern-based module.
